<section id="page-profile" class="page-profile">
<div class="container">
  <header class="section-header">
  <h2 class="section-title">Personal Profile</h2>
  <div class="spacer"></div>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Entrepreneurial Web Developer and Founder, currently in Chiang Mai</p>
  </header>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="profile">
        <%= image_tag 'profile-photo.png', alt: 'profile' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9">
      <p>Originally from London, UK, I have lived in the South of France, Barcelona, Berlin, Malta, Phuket and currently Chiang Mai.</p>

      <p>While in Berlin I founded 1000jobboersen.de which at one point reached over 150 employees, $1 mil monthly revenue and eventually merged with softgarden.de. Since then I helped found GoHiring, another company in the online hiring space. Now I'm contracting remotely, currently for GrooveHQ, the worlds best simple customer support SaaS app, based in the US. When I'm not doing that, I'm hacking on <a href="https://github.com/mattbeedle/capsule_crm">open</a> <a href="https://github.com/mattbeedle/usda-nutrient-database">source</a>, building new products (like <a href="http://vegan.io">Vegan.io</a>), learning new things and totally failing at <a href="http://blog.mattbeedle.name">blogging</a> regularly.</p>

      <p>I'm proficient in Java, PHP, Ruby and Javascript (Ruby and Javascript preferred). I also have some knowledge of C, Python, Scala and Go. I'm fairly active in open source. You can check out my code on <a href="http://github.com/mattbeedle">GitHub</a>.</p>

      <p>For a more detailed work history my <a href="http://linkedin.com/in/mattbeedle">LinkedIn profile</a> has all the information you need. You can also download a hard copy of my resume <a href="/resume.pdf">here</a>.</p>

      <p>I'm always interested in helping early stage startups get their product to launch and build a great development team, so if you need some help there, please <a href="#page-contact">give me a shout.</a>. I'm also extremely interested in distributed, self managed teams, using real time commuication tools and reporting.</p>

      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section><!-- profile ends -->
