      <p>GrooveHQ is one of the worlds best known customer service tools. It allows teams to manage incoming email and social media without looking like they're using a support app. I was one of the first developers although now there are many. I've been helping with scaling issues, automating local environments with Docker, getting shit done and migrating away from a monolithic RoR app to AWS Lambda, GraphQL, ReactJS and Redux.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
